South African Central Bank’s Marcus Comments on Growth Outlook

-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 
2011-07-21T13:17:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/south-african-central-bank-s-marcus-comments-on-growth-outlook.html
South African Reserve Bank Governor
Gill Marcus made the following comments on the growth outlook
after a meeting of the bank’s monetary policy committee in
 Pretoria  today.  “The forecast of the bank for GDP growth for 2011 and 2012
remains unchanged at 3.7 percent and 3.9 percent respectively.  “Growth in 2014 is expected to be 4.4 percent.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mike Cohen in Cape Town at 
 mcohen21@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Barden at   barden@bloomberg.net  